{"tid":2068905,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"非洲國家迦納向美國非裔人士發出邀請 表示歡迎回家","createTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T12:00:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"cb751930313fcb489bc4ce8ffa66c86795b2b396","tid":2068905,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"即時新聞／綜合報導〕<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，迦納文化部長芭芭拉（Barbara Oteng-Gyasi）近日對美國非裔族群喊話，表示該國持續張開雙臂，邀請這些分隔數百年的兄弟姊妹們回家，她說，「你們不必待在不喜歡的地方，你們永遠可以選擇，非洲正等著你們回家」。<br />\n<br />\n芭芭拉進一步抨擊美國的種族主義，將其形容作「致命的流行病」，她說，這種疾病至今已有400多年歷史，而迦納希望這些遠在美國的手足們獲得治癒。<br />\n<br />\n迦納作為非洲社會較安定、經濟結構較合理的國家，去年推出「回歸之年」（The Year of the Return）政策<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&d=u0uYB5UElWTGJsHKTdw4wRBMzzOW1qmypsfK5hxWA9U%3D&h=251e9c5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3201376&h=70018ce2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3201376</a>"},{"pid":"e6b39065cf2fa93834554f8b0f1bf444fe11af11","tid":2068905,"uid":53003,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:32:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/images/6bd479b16f0be25fab987caa545c958e/tenor.gif?itemid=16980099\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia1.tenor.com%2Fimages%2F6bd479b16f0be25fab987caa545c958e%2Ftenor.gif%3Fitemid%3D16980099&h=2d4b7a0f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ced3aa338a66f6f581c03e1a41455fc3d0bea2a","tid":2068905,"uid":81698,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T04:37:52.000Z","msg":"班友彩你都傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be